{"tid":703902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上海自貿區而家點？","createTime":"2018-06-16T04:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T14:06:00.000Z","uid":128261,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1f907a16f72198916b6df0b5a200d70f026f7c2c","tid":703902,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"近一兩年完全無人提過<br />\n仲記得2013年推出果陣又話會取代香港又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdd20b27323a1ece54208f2f254dc9e684211ad","tid":703902,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"2000年嘅時候已經話要取代香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb9dbdec877dae5b60918f1954aeabaf9ac0a6b","tid":703902,"uid":2442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"宜家講大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea837d2c2d5e9484a849780a652e6fa306732d8b","tid":703902,"uid":10692,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"442310ce063e1c16fed3bd643a31777331973abc","tid":703902,"uid":143915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"好成功 超越紐約倫敦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb6823e90db36aa14ec80152eb06306d8db93ec","tid":703902,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"前海都話取代香港又盛<br />\n<br />\n乜都唔得, 又講乜叉大灣區<br />\n<br />\n支狗一味口號多多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82065b215b658842f6618e7da05f5f8bddae63c5","tid":703902,"uid":146621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"自慰區就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef62deb06436215c8484d37efca2cc9fd241c38","tid":703902,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"當年CCTVB吹到好勁 會秒殺香港的"},{"pid":"7f74de237685d3fcae20e7c2bd07d57632f8afc0","tid":703902,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8eb6823e90db36aa14ec80152eb06306d8db93ec","tid":703902,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"前海都話取代香港又盛<br />\n<br />\n乜都唔得, 又講乜叉大灣區<br />\n<br />\n支狗一味口號多多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"前海依定點? 定係爛地一塊? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86563c7102905e9059ae922c0c13f3de9e22d66f","tid":703902,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"隔離國家既野關你鬼事咩"},{"pid":"01f794fb07848f477e35c3ce36285151da810883","tid":703902,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"中國自由貿易試驗區（英語：China Pilot Free Trade Zone），是中國設立的自由貿易園區，是指在主權國家或者地區的關境以外，劃出特定的區域，准許外國商品豁免關稅自由進出。2011年，中央政府初步確立了在青島、天津、上海和深圳等地建立自由貿易區的規劃與設想。[1]<br />\n<br />\n2013年9月29日，上海自由貿易區最先掛牌成立，成為中國第一個自由貿易試驗區。[2]2015年4月21日，廣東自貿區、天津自貿區、福建自貿區相繼揭牌。2017年4月1日，遼寧自貿區、浙江自貿區、河南自貿區、湖北自貿區、重慶自貿區、四川自貿區、陝西自貿區揭牌成立。<br />\n<br />\n全部超越曬香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18d6d0d5a64bb78bb2cb07b3e4fbdf563554061","tid":703902,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86563c7102905e9059ae922c0c13f3de9e22d66f","tid":703902,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"隔離國家既野關你鬼事咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"唔討論得？<br />\n咁係咪美國歐洲既事都唔講得？<br />\n點先算關事？"},{"pid":"509b16aa258112dc3af224460c9ec611daaec48a","tid":703902,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.baidu.com/from=844b/s?word=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%87%AA%E8%B4%B8%E5%8C%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%B2%A1%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%86&amp;rq=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BF%E5%8D%80&amp;sa=brs_1&amp;rsf=1&amp;pqid=10344408316283068234&amp;ant_ct=E4S7POY6hFOkvz7iMZNEPTkx%2BzTVpprRfCXoVl2BSWB%2FJEve9bAf3G0LvlRt%2BHRC&amp;ms=1&amp;rqid=10344408316283068234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.baidu.com%2Ffrom%3D844b%2Fs%3Fword%3D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B4%25B8%25E5%258C%25BA%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%25B2%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%2586%26rq%3D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%26sa%3Dbrs_1%26rsf%3D1%26pqid%3D10344408316283068234%26ant_ct%3DE4S7POY6hFOkvz7iMZNEPTkx%252BzTVpprRfCXoVl2BSWB%252FJEve9bAf3G0LvlRt%252BHRC%26ms%3D1%26rqid%3D10344408316283068234&d=bTxF3GTHIY4ejja7HVfaoUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e010ad13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.baidu.com/from=844b/s?word=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%87%AA%E8%B4%B8%E5%8C%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%B2%A1%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%86&amp;rq=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%87%AA%E8%B2%BF%E5%8D%80&amp;sa=brs_1&amp;rsf=1&amp;pqid=10344408316283068234&amp;ant_ct=E4S7POY6hFOkvz7iMZNEPTkx%2BzTVpprRfCXoVl2BSWB%2FJEve9bAf3G0LvlRt%2BHRC&amp;ms=1&amp;rqid=10344408316283068234</a>"},{"pid":"ed546bc7ee7288ed381b2d78568d77eb79b23fc6","tid":703902,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T10:18:25.000Z","msg":"唔少公司進註 但好似無咩聲氣？"},{"pid":"5b86aff988f1b06ee91b17156327e0b89e156c40","tid":703902,"uid":52358,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"fef62deb06436215c8484d37efca2cc9fd241c38","tid":703902,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"當年CCTVB吹到好勁 會秒殺香港的"},"citedBy":0,"